headline: 3 High-Yield Dividend Stocks Wall Street Thinks Will Soar 41% or More in 2025
summary: Analysts might have found just the stocks to buy, too.  Here are three high-yield dividend stocks Wall Street thinks will soar 41% or more in 2025.  AES (NYSE: AES) ranks as the top seller of renewable power to corporate customers and operates two of the fastest-growing utilities in the U.S. The company owns hydroelectric, solar, and wind power-generation facilities, as well as natural gas, coal, and pet-coke or oil facilities.
